longDescription:
Aurekai MCP server exposes the full Aurekai native runtime to any MCP-compatible host. Includes: akai doctor, manifest validation, artifact inspection, feature queries, semantic search, proof bundle export (.akrun.json, .akproof.json, .aktrace.jsonl, .akfeatures.json, .akcost.json), and the complete family of 89 Aurekai binary operators.

Install via npx:
```
npx -y @aurekai/mcp
```

Or add to Claude Desktop `mcpServers`:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "aurekai": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "@aurekai/mcp"]
    }
  }
}
```
